  "texts": [
    "Instructors should experiment with simulation prompts in their subject matter to better understand how the models react to their instructions.",
    "As with any AI exercise, instructor involvement, feedback, and oversight are critical.",
    "Teaching someone else can help you learn.",
    "Students who teach others engage deeply in the material and can gain insights into the gaps in their knowledge, as they monitor their own understanding (Kirschner & Hendrick, 2020).",
    "Known as the protégé effect\" students who teach others develop higher comprehension and a deeper, more persistent understanding of the material (Fiorella & Mayer, 2013)."
  ],
